{{!--
================================================================================
  CLIENTS (Agency logo strip) — `{{> clients }}`

  Renders a grey strip of partner / client logos (Start Bootstrap “Agency”
  pattern). Pass data on your Handlebars context from `getContentHtml`, a
  controller, or route payload.

  Omit `clients`, or set it to `[]`: the bundled Start Bootstrap SVG logos
  (Microsoft, Google, Facebook, IBM) show so local previews work with no data.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  CONTEXT FIELDS

  clientsSectionClass  (optional)  Extra classes on the outer wrapper.
                                  Default: `py-5` (only this class if unset).

  clients              (optional)  Array of logo links. Each item:

      href         string   Link target; use `#!` or `/` if non-navigating
      src          string   Image URL (site `public/` path or absolute URL)
      alt          string   Short description for the image (required for a11y)
      ariaLabel    string   Optional; sets `aria-label` on the `<a>` when the
                            visible text is only the logo graphic

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  EXAMPLE (conceptual shape for a TypeScript controller)

    const clients = [
      {
        href: 'https://example.com/partner',
        src: '/assets/logos/partner-a.svg',
        alt: 'Partner A',
        ariaLabel: 'Partner A home',
      },
      { href: '#!', src: '/assets/logos/partner-b.svg', alt: 'Partner B' },
    ]

    website.getContentHtml('landing')( {
      title: 'Home',
      clients,
    } )

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  LAYOUT

  • Each item is `col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3` (four across on medium+ screens).
  • Add or remove array entries to change the count; the grid wraps naturally.
================================================================================
--}}
<div class="{{#if clientsSectionClass}}{{clientsSectionClass}}{{else}}py-5{{/if}}">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      {{#each clients}}
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
          <a href="{{#if href}}{{href}}{{else}}#!{{/if}}">
            <img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto" src="{{src}}" alt="{{alt}}"
              {{#if ariaLabel}}aria-label="{{ariaLabel}}"{{/if}} />
          </a>
        </div>
      {{else}}
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
          <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto"
              src="https://startbootstrap.github.io/startbootstrap-agency/assets/img/logos/microsoft.svg" alt="Microsoft logo"
              aria-label="Microsoft Logo" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
          <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto"
              src="https://startbootstrap.github.io/startbootstrap-agency/assets/img/logos/google.svg" alt="Google logo"
              aria-label="Google Logo" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
          <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto"
              src="https://startbootstrap.github.io/startbootstrap-agency/assets/img/logos/facebook.svg" alt="Facebook logo"
              aria-label="Facebook Logo" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 my-3">
          <a href="#!"><img class="img-fluid img-brand d-block mx-auto"
              src="https://startbootstrap.github.io/startbootstrap-agency/assets/img/logos/ibm.svg" alt="IBM logo"
              aria-label="IBM Logo" /></a>
        </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
